OL,3,CFewer visits to dying patients as UK
OL,4,Chospices hit crisis point
OL,6,FUK hospices are in crisis and their
OL,7,Ffinancial stability is at a critical
OL,8,Fpoint, leaders have warned.
OL,10,FHospice UK, which represents more than
OL,11,F200 hospices across the UK, said the
OL,12,Fsector's finances are in their worst
OL,13,Fstate for 20 years.
OL,15,FAt least a fifth of hospices have cut
OL,16,Ftheir services in the last year or are
OL,17,Fplanning to do so, according to the
OL,18,Fnational charity.
