OL,3,CFewer visits to dying patients as UK
OL,4,Chospices hit crisis point
OL,6,FThis means inpatient beds are being
OL,7,Fcut, staff are being made redundant
OL,8,Fand community services are being
OL,9,Frestricted, with fewer visits to dying
OL,10,Fpatients in their own homes.
OL,12,FPressure on hospices has been growing,
OL,13,Faccording to Hospice UK, which says
OL,14,F"modest" state funding has not kept
OL,15,Fpace with increasing running costs.
OL,17,FIt is now urging the public to write
OL,18,Fto their local MP calling for
OL,19,Fincreased government support.
