OL,3,CFewer visits to dying patients as UK
OL,4,Chospices hit crisis point
OL,6,FToby Porter, chief executive of
OL,7,FHospice UK, said "the timing couldn't
OL,8,Fbe worse", with demand for end-of-life
OL,9,Fcare increasing.
OL,11,FHe added: "When hospices cut services,
OL,12,Fpatients are pushed back into the NHS,
OL,13,Fultimately costing the taxpayer more.
OL,15,F"We know that our health and social
OL,16,Fcare services in the UK are under
OL,17,Fimmense strain, yet thousands of
OL,18,Fhospice staff are desperate to help,
OL,19,Fif only hospices could be properly
OL,20,Ffunded."
