OL,6,FJeremy Lune, chief executive of
OL,7,FProspect Hospice in Swindon, said: "At
OL,8,FProspect Hospice, we've had to reduce
OL,9,Fthe number of beds in our inpatient
OL,10,Funit to six, despite having room for
OL,11,F12.
OL,13,F"This decision isn't enough, as we
OL,14,Fstill face a #1 million deficit. The
OL,15,Fneed for our palliative and end-of-
OL,16,Flife care is growing, while funding is
OL,17,Fdwindling, creating an unsustainable
OL,18,Fsituation."
