OL,6,FEmma May Ward, clinical nurse
OL,7,Fspecialist for Marie Curie in the West
OL,8,FMidlands, said: "Every day my team and
OL,9,FI see the devastating impacts of
OL,10,Foverloaded and underfunded end-of-life
OL,11,Fcare services in hospices and
OL,12,Fdelivered in people's homes.
OL,14,F"Increasingly, we are finding families
OL,15,Fat crisis point, distressed and not
OL,16,Fknowing where to turn, often forced to
OL,17,Fcall 999 or go to A&E when they don't
OL,18,Fneed or want to.
