OL,6,F"Too many people are falling through
OL,7,Fthe cracks, and too many people are
OL,8,Fdying in avoidable pain."
OL,10,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,11,Fspokesman said: "We want a society
OL,12,Fwhere every person, their families,
OL,13,Fand carers, receive high quality,
OL,14,Fcompassionate care, from diagnosis
OL,15,Fthrough to end of life.
