OL,6,F"The government is going to shift the
OL,7,Ffocus of healthcare out of the
OL,8,Fhospital and into the community. We
OL,9,Frecognise that the care system,
OL,10,Fincluding hospices, will play a vital
OL,11,Frole in doing this.
OL,13,F"We are going to grip the social care
OL,14,Fcrisis, starting with the workforce by
OL,15,Fdelivering a new deal for care workers.
OL,17,F"We will also take steps to create a
OL,18,FNational Care Service underpinned by
OL,19,Fnational standards, delivering
OL,20,Fconsistency of care across the
OL,21,Fcountry."
